AGI - The Governor of Florida, Republican Ron DeSantis, has signed a law that makes the climate crisis no longer one of the main priorities of the state, refusing, as stated on its official X profile, "the agenda of radical green fanatics". The signature on three bills on energy sources, foreign investments and raw materials will hold windmills (windmills) away from the beaches of the state and will serve, among other things, to "report mental health in our approach to energy>", added DeSantis.
&nbsp;
<div </div
&nbsp;
